[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    46[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   # context-aware resolution detection (e.g., checking whether the marker
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    47[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   # modifies the condition or describes its current status).
